#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:39
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The TNEF File Viewer is an application for <ulink url=\"https://en.wikipedia."
"org/wiki/TNEF\">TNEF</ulink> mail attachments."
msgstr ""
"TNEF सञ्चिकादर्शकः <ulink url=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/TNEF\">TNEF</"
"ulink> मेलसंलग्नकानां कृते एकः अनुप्रयोगः अस्ति ।"

#. Tag: keyword
#: index.docbook:42
#, no-c-format
