#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:50
#, no-c-format
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "आमुख"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:52
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The TNEF File Viewer allows to handle easily mail attachments using the TNEF "
"format. Those attachments are usually found in mails coming from <trademark "
"class=\"registered\">Microsoft</trademark> mail servers and embed the mail "
"properties as well as the actual attachments."
msgstr ""
"TNEF File Viewer इत्यनेन TNEF प्रारूपस्य उपयोगेन मेल-संलग्नकान् सुलभतया नियन्त्रयितुं शक्यते "
"। ते संलग्नकानि प्रायः <trademark class=\"registered\">Microsoft</trademark> "
"मेलसर्वरतः आगच्छन्तीषु मेलेषु दृश्यन्ते तथा च मेलगुणान् तथा च वास्तविकसंलग्नकान् एम्बेड् कुर्वन्ति"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:55
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"An attachment in TNEF format is most often named <filename>winmail.dat</"
"filename> or <filename>win.dat</filename>."
msgstr ""
"TNEF प्रारूपेण संलग्नस्य अधिकतया <filename>winmail.dat</filename> अथवा "
"<filename>win.dat</filename> इति नाम भवति ।"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:58
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>TNEF Main Window</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>TNEF मुख्यविण्डो</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:64
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>TNEF Main Window</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>TNEF मुख्यविण्डो</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:69
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This utility program allows to perform various operations on those "
"attachments:"
msgstr "एषः उपयोगिताकार्यक्रमः तेषु संलग्नकेषु विविधानि कार्याणि कर्तुं शक्नोति:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:71
#, no-c-format
msgid "View/open attachments with associated applications."
msgstr "सम्बद्धैः अनुप्रयोगैः सह संलग्नकानि पश्यन्तु/उद्घाटयन्तु।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:72
#, no-c-format
msgid "Extract actual attachments"
msgstr "वास्तविकं आसक्तिं निष्कासयन्तु"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:73
#, no-c-format
msgid "View message properties (TNEF/MAPI)"
msgstr "सन्देशगुणान् पश्यन्तु (TNEF/MAPI)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:74
#, no-c-format
msgid "View/extract message formatted text (in RTF format)"
msgstr "सन्देशस्वरूपितं पाठं पश्यन्तु/निष्कासयन्तु (RTF प्रारूपेण)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:77
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kmail; automatically shows the content of a TNEF attachment. You can open "
"or save the attachments using the actions in the context menu."
msgstr ""
"&kmail; स्वयमेव TNEF संलग्नकस्य सामग्रीं दर्शयति । सन्दर्भमेनूमध्ये क्रियाणां उपयोगेन "
"संलग्नकानि उद्घाटयितुं वा रक्षितुं वा शक्नुवन्ति ।"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:80
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>TNEF attachment in &kmail;</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>&kmail;</screeninfo> इत्यस्मिन् TNEF संलग्नम्"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:86
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>TNEF attachment in &kmail;</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>&kmail;</phrase> इत्यस्मिन् TNEF संलग्नता"

